1cGy Binned DVHs + >80 other DICOM variables tracked
Records a sample of the distribution of PTV-OAR Distances
Using SciPy, distances between all PTV-OAR point pairs are calculated in 3D.
The min, mean, median, and max of these numbers are recorded in the database.
